# 🧠 Next Chatbot (AI-Powered Chat Assistant)

A plug-and-play AI chatbot assistant for Next.js powered by [Google Gemini](https://ai.google.dev/). Just install, configure your API key, and you're good to go!

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✨ Powered by [@google/generative-ai](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@google/generative-ai)
- ⚙️ Easy to integrate into any Next.js project
- 💬 Supports custom chat history/context
- 🔐 Works with your `.env` configuration
- 🧩 Extendable with custom UI or logic

---

## 📦 Installation

### 1. Install the required package:

```bash
npm install @google/generative-ai
